# MGATBC
MGAT is used for brain disease diagnostic analysis based on fMRI and can also be used for classification tasks of graph data.
# Requirement
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

Note: The operating environment of knn_adj.py is requirements_(knn_adj).txt.

# Data
In order to use your own data, you have to provide

an T by N BOLD signal matrix for every subject (N is the number of nodes,T is the time series length).

# RESEARCH PAPERS USING THIS SOFTWARE:
-  Renping Yu, Cong Pan, Xuan Fei, Mingming Chen, and Dinggang Shen, Fellow, IEEE, Multi-Graph Attention Networks with Bilinear Convolution for Diagnosis of Schizophrenia, IEEE Journal of Biomedical and Health Informatics

